                                    li: a(href=item): img(plx-img src=item)
                    h1.title Minigames
                    h3.subtitle Spruce up your server with the prettiest chat minigames!
                    .infobox
                        p Build your own virtual casino with our set of minigames, both single and multi player. We got the fanciest Blackjack, Slot Machine, and Roulette game. As well as some more fun and unusual minigames like Flag Guesser, Black Metal Band Guesser, and of course a Trivia Game too.
                    
                    hr.plx-divider-icon
                    
                    h1.title Solid Economy System
                    h3.subtitle Your efforts are protected!
                    
                    .infobox(plx-lightbox).buffer
